<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #F3F4F6; padding: 20px;">

  <div style="border: 1px solid #002130; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="background-color: #002130; font-weight: bold; color: #E3E4E7; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem;">
      IPC Meeting Invitation
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 30px; font-size: 1.2rem;">
      <p>
        Dear <%= @employee.person.full_name %>,
      </p>

      <p>
        You are kindly invited to attend the Internal Procurement Committee meeting.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Requisition:</strong> <em><%= @requisition.purpose %></em><br>
        <strong>Date:</strong> <%= @meeting_date.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %><br>
        <strong>Time:</strong> <%= @meeting_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %><br>
        <strong>Venue:</strong> Conference Room<br>
        
      </p>

      <p>
        Your participation and expertise are highly valued for this important procurement review.
      </p>

      <p>
        Kindly confirm your attendance by replying to this email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #6c757d;">
    <p>This is an automated notification. <%= Time.current.year %></p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>

